{"tid":1185356,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又贏！特朗普開始限制中國留學生簽證","createTime":"2019-06-04T08:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T13:11:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"574c91651ffef9d81b918b5717f8ec30e9b3ff90","tid":1185356,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:31:36.000Z","msg":"美國著名財經媒體彭博報道，美國總統特朗普發動的貿易戰，已從科技進一步延伸到頂尖人才，美國已開始限制學生簽證！<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，最近幾周有幾位中國研究生和學者發現，美國的學術和工作環境愈來愈不友善。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府最新數據顯示，今年首3個月中國政府資助學生拒簽的比例增至13.5%，較去年同期3.2%大增。<br />\n<br />\n有麻省理工學院中國博士生候選人透露，以前年度學生簽證續簽需要3個星期，現在拖延了幾個月。不但學生拒簽比例增加，研究人員也遭遣散，當中涉及「千人計劃」的參與者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190604/bkn-20190604161257714-0604_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190604%2Fbkn-20190604161257714-0604_00842_001.html&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgnNo2vAooDXMO4YLrfRUzdI%3D&h=b68d4e1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190604/bkn-20190604161257714-0604_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8010f4b05b28c1accae528fdd8c6993b4a0e8d32","tid":1185356,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d02233f21b5d5b3d0bd88004f8debf683a6ac49","tid":1185356,"uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OXwS2Kv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOXwS2Kv.gif&h=93b8161d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"315e1222c3d122f7ca080328cd6a066bab3f06dc","tid":1185356,"uid":237562,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:32:53.000Z","msg":"建議以間諜罪調查所有支那流學生"},{"pid":"f09917735e89fd69d1533ada0d039f40f895ecd4","tid":1185356,"uid":65300,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:33:07.000Z","msg":"入左千人